%md
# Setup

paragraphs.title: Retrieve the files from devuser
paragraphs.text:
%sh
rm -r /tmp/cloudair
mkdir /tmp/cloudair
cp /home/devuser/data/cloudair/* /tmp/cloudair/

msg.data: rm: cannot remove ‘/tmp/cloudair’: No such file or directory

paragraphs.title: List the directory /tmp/cloudair
paragraphs.text:
%sh
ls /tmp/cloudair/

paragraphs.title: Use bunzip2 to extract the files
paragraphs.text:
%sh
bunzip2 /tmp/cloudair/eu_country.csv.bz2
bunzip2 /tmp/cloudair/sale.csv.bz2
bunzip2 /tmp/cloudair/us_customer.csv.bz2
bunzip2 /tmp/cloudair/ww_customer.csv.bz2

paragraphs.title: List the contents of /tmp/cloudair
paragraphs.text:
%sh
ls /tmp/cloudair

paragraphs.title: Make the directories in HDFS
paragraphs.text:
%sh
sudo -u hdfs hdfs dfs -rm -r -skipTrash /data/cloudair
sudo -u hdfs hdfs dfs -mkdir /data/cloudair
sudo -u hdfs hdfs dfs -chmod -R 777 /data/cloudair

hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /data/cloudair/eu_country
hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /data/cloudair/sale
hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /data/cloudair/us_customer
hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /data/cloudair/ww_customer

paragraphs.title: Copy the datafiles in HDFS
paragraphs.text:
%sh
hdfs dfs -put /tmp/cloudair/eu_country.csv /data/cloudair/eu_country/
hdfs dfs -put /tmp/cloudair/sale.csv /data/cloudair/sale/
hdfs dfs -put /tmp/cloudair/us_customer.csv /data/cloudair/us_customer/
hdfs dfs -put /tmp/cloudair/ww_customer.csv /data/cloudair/ww_customer/

paragraphs.title: Grant Hive access to /data/cloudair
paragraphs.text:
%sh
sudo -u hdfs hdfs dfs -chown -R hive /data/cloudair

paragraphs.title: List the contents of HDFS /data/cloudair
paragraphs.text:
%sh
hdfs dfs -ls -h -R /data/cloudair
